ato Grosso州的亚马逊雨林，长期以来一直是数十年来与森林砍伐&lt;i&gt;摄影师的核心：Pablo Porciuncula/AFP&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;巴西计划&lt;/strong&gt;通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=924a4f40d9704bdf9eb32601e09a6c54&amp;amp;_e=dil_hCy1VrFounNjyI3YU8aDKS0Du-GpivlIuhsNGZLU6uNGf7IAD0JGsYFIeOZoKnMbKOu97IRX28idAUMernWQHM3NH7zmreNrcnlFxs7H45R7NYSutZtD5ri7jxmD7E1oqdxsJQ1hI7jj-9y-GwfbWXdsFB4hz80ZGiUbGfbwFJDOunfVlhP09Hjjls_zUF13ojU-niqWuEoKthVXDWd6mNxsAUlPBCvNLmR1_PQTr7dPBfeBesqTn_b7fSMz2y4uySvMfOGPw5G1g8jeuaedevN7oy4xAHwHzmXFe4JuUdu8Mr36lGcgoW9_8GOsIpUFqTCV6DJf2rSliDmd58u3DccbevDyfkZJ0anTjN5OPjbeuCvoG9XQ_E2VZehORXX589C_4hWuWMQRN7OSdQabySJJ_e8v7QA3fjjcWWnJS6AJCW_jFYEI8CDCU2gy7hwnHK_bm6djMMXjGSJnrqYlrs-q_8dzS6reY30h8_QizTTOotiVrksCVVK1AiIf-uiIBffkeKOviZn1EXqHrwgUZLwtYUUIKuA2cuj47_jDziOb6nTOQKmwyecT7TUeg3Es0rRcO0b30dfKUPdBZZaSbXe-sUu4lt7iE94jm1XYlWhOnAP4oJvaSiPzNTDqER8yI9S5CtyXMLBsqw9PFrCmkOrlH8kf-UtzL7hfuzYliFdTqqcumubv139SF92MUdevdvE331ZvoCABpFcTlVC3l-kUUA8eXjS9PmXovUlbDZEX6vNoDzr5fKLd_ivIybJkIgs42lvCv23XZq6Gzq4OcOjvJpIH-vWyjkTIkVco-psVIJ8Pq8gdHl1-5Dhfvf0kX2XZJsC8BsaibcD2PA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;利用华尔街的财务能力&lt;/a&gt;来保护热带森林，在COP30（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=924a4f40d9704bdf9eb32601e09a6c54&amp;amp;_e=dil_hCy1VrFounNjyI3YU8aDKS0Du-GpivlIuhsNGZJivFz4L7BXSNjxA2eSYe2cCSD94KD-dcHZ6Mr8zCo-iHFnm6V9kkZJGrK-OniBUfkup1fXnrSM-Ywqp47hvRAA977w4QguZ2XGTZ4i3lMvLNLuDt_pWS6Dz8lhP3ts5AU2uKpP-ybXpqBjZ64XsNpDOP3PiABFo97lYjMlIMZI76hzBnVutqYHflb4HySVzjd2753OkGa7G-6F9PXJc15ZDsz0yrEoenl46X6-gQnYrLYALLlqgxf-hccjIAsBeZ7A-wNOVOXp9t2QMtlqReGep8fMgPvK-b8AQkIbmCSsBm3RdggoVUz43v4U21nwnkapNq_03Xgpa7qH3F-tdlVNf3A12NckTDpRUhHaHgUFDwfN6k8f1j2zX9RSuoCZEsJqenwfcflkZQr83s-41ChbPW8MmFF0fzehSKBCCDB_S3h5wcXyKd-ixWMWeDX0Is1Dpdi4aZn-TS4G4jqizxNiOUvzmnxpDFVvc4N1OGdPTTgh